@abdymojab
> Screen goes blank at a point during playback. Reloading doesn’t help because the issue persists after a few seconds of playback again.

Hi. Works fine on my ipad. Which filter breaks the site? After changing filters settings, do not close AdGuard window 30-60 seconds, because iOS will breaks configuration process.

